name: Continent of Kalisk
description: The continent of Kalisk, which consists of 12 countries. Kalisk is one of 5 continents on the planet of Tez. The continent of Kalisk is known for its various climates and its various peoples. There are three distinctive races that live on this continent. They are the Arveinos peoples, Ziremian peoples, and the Asachren peoples. Zoom in! 3096x1548
